This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4603

launch your Emacs Client from vim, and capture a file or store link with org mode.

Org mode is for keeping notes, maintaining TODO lists, planning projects, and authoring documents with a fast and effective plain-text system.

http://orgmode.org/

key map:

<A-n> : capture a file

<A-l> : store a link

